            <title>[LU-2905] fsx fails on SLES11SP2 2.4 client</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2905</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Running:  fsx -c 100 -N 100000 -l 5M -o 1M /mnt/fs/foo/testfile&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Fails with SIGBUS during memcpy from mmap&apos;ed memory (line 875)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I can&apos;t find fault with the fsx code, and this test works on other platforms.  It&apos;s reproducable about 50% of the time.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
